        <briefdescription>
<para>Creates and registers an owning resource. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Heap-allocates a resource of type T, stores it in `owned_` via <ref refid="structhelios_1_1core_1_1memory_1_1ErasedUnique" kindref="compound">ErasedUnique</ref>, and indexes it in `fastAccess_`. If T derives from <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1Manager" kindref="compound">Manager</ref> or <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1CommandBuffer" kindref="compound">CommandBuffer</ref>, it is additionally tracked in the corresponding iteration list.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The resource type. Must derive from <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1world_1_1Manager" kindref="compound">Manager</ref> or <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1runtime_1_1messaging_1_1command_1_1CommandBuffer" kindref="compound">CommandBuffer</ref>. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Args</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Constructor argument types.</para>
